accessibility.text: Person in Wheelchair 2 - Lesson 1 - Noise and Buttons.png

Because they all like different vehicles, they most likely dont meld well with each other and would rather find other people that have similar interests to them.  For example, the person who likes trains might try to find another person who likes trains to talk to instead of talking to someone who likes cars.
